    "content": {
      "rendered": "<p><a href=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/01/must-see-nonprofit-infographics.jpg\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"alignright size-medium wp-image-15382\" style=\"border: 1px solid black;\" alt=\"must see nonprofit infographics\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/01/must-see-nonprofit-infographics-300x300.jpg?resize=300%2C300\" width=\"300\" height=\"300\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/01/must-see-nonprofit-infographics.jpg?resize=300%2C300&amp;ssl=1 300w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/01/must-see-nonprofit-infographics.jpg?resize=150%2C150&amp;ssl=1 150w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/01/must-see-nonprofit-infographics.jpg?resize=200%2C200&amp;ssl=1 200w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/01/must-see-nonprofit-infographics.jpg?resize=75%2C75&amp;ssl=1 75w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/01/must-see-nonprofit-infographics.jpg?w=500&amp;ssl=1 500w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 300px) 100vw, 300px\" /></a>Without a doubt, 2013 was the year of visual content &#8212; particularly infographics. With tens of millions of brands now tweeting, posting, and sharing content online on a daily basis, to get your message to stand out from the clutter brands need to communicate more often their key messages in visual format. That said, below are 19 infographics useful to nonprofit communications and development staff. Like everyone, we&#8217;re inundated as well and increasingly need to see important data about nonprofit technology trends in visual format.</p>\n<hr />\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\">1. Why Smart Social Marketers Think Mobile First<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.unifiedsocial.com/mobile-social-marketing/#i.k73ae32gieu8q7\">View Full Infographic</a></h2>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http://www.unifiedsocial.com/mobile-social-marketing/#i.k73ae32gieu8q7\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-15325\" style=\"border: 1px solid black;\" alt=\"why smart marketers think mobile first infographic\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/01/why-smart-marketers-think-mobile-first-infographic.png?resize=600%2C494\" width=\"600\" height=\"494\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/01/why-smart-marketers-think-mobile-first-infographic.png?w=600&amp;ssl=1 600w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/01/why-smart-marketers-think-mobile-first-infographic.png?resize=300%2C247&amp;ssl=1 300w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" /></a></p>\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\">2. Nonprofit Communications Trends 2014<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.nonprofitmarketingguide.com/blog/2014/01/08/2014-nonprofit-communications-trends-report-infographic/\">View Full Infographic</a></h2>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http://www.nonprofitmarketingguide.com/blog/2014/01/08/2014-nonprofit-communications-trends-report-infographic/\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-15292\" style=\"border: 1px solid black;\" alt=\"Nonprofit Communication Trends 2014\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/01/Nonprofit-Communication-Trends-2014.png?resize=600%2C438\" width=\"600\" height=\"438\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/01/Nonprofit-Communication-Trends-2014.png?w=600&amp;ssl=1 600w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/01/Nonprofit-Communication-Trends-2014.png?resize=300%2C219&amp;ssl=1 300w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" /></a></p>\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\">3. #GivingTuesday 2013<br />\n<a href=\"http://blog.techimpact.org/infographic-giving-tuesday-2013/\">View Full Infographic</a></h2>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http://blog.techimpact.org/infographic-giving-tuesday-2013/\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter\" style=\"border: 1px solid black;\" alt=\"GivingTuesday\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/01/GivingTuesday.png?resize=600%2C450\" width=\"600\" height=\"450\" /></a></p>\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\">4. What&#8217;s Trending with Foundations and Social Media?<br />\n<a href=\"http://glasspockets.org/glasspockets-gallery/foundations-and-social-media-infographic\">View Full Infographic</a></h2>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http://glasspockets.org/glasspockets-gallery/foundations-and-social-media-infographic\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-15307\" style=\"border: 1px solid black;\" alt=\"Foundation and Social Media Infographic\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/01/Foundation-and-Social-Media-Infographic.png?resize=600%2C537\" width=\"600\" height=\"537\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/01/Foundation-and-Social-Media-Infographic.png?w=600&amp;ssl=1 600w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/01/Foundation-and-Social-Media-Infographic.png?resize=300%2C268&amp;ssl=1 300w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" /></a></p>\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\">5. The Future of Social Activism<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.columnfivemedia.com/work-items/infographic-2012-social-activism\">View Full Infographic</a></h2>\n<p><a href=\"http://www.columnfivemedia.com/work-items/infographic-2012-social-activism\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter\" style=\"border: 1px solid black;\" alt=\"Future of Social Activism\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/01/Future-of-Social-Activism.png?resize=600%2C513\" width=\"600\" height=\"513\" /></a></p>\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\">6. Social Media 2013<br />\n<a href=\"http://blog.digitalinsights.in/social-media-facts-and-statistics-2013/0560387.html\">View Full Infographic</a></h2>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http://blog.digitalinsights.in/social-media-facts-and-statistics-2013/0560387.html\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter\" style=\"border: 1px solid black;\" alt=\"social media 2013 infographic\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/01/social-media-2013-infographic.png?resize=600%2C403\" width=\"600\" height=\"403\" /></a></p>\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\">7. How Much Do Nonprofits Invest in Social Media?<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.verticalresponse.com/blog/non-profits-investing-more-time-money-social-media/\">View Full Infographic</a></h2>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http://www.verticalresponse.com/blog/non-profits-investing-more-time-money-social-media/\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-15329\" style=\"border: 1px solid black;\" alt=\"how much do nonprofits invest in social media infographic\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/01/how-much-do-nonprofits-invest-in-social-media-infographic.png?resize=600%2C404\" width=\"600\" height=\"404\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/01/how-much-do-nonprofits-invest-in-social-media-infographic.png?w=600&amp;ssl=1 600w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/01/how-much-do-nonprofits-invest-in-social-media-infographic.png?resize=300%2C202&amp;ssl=1 300w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" /></a></p>\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\">8. Ridiculously Exhaustive Social Media Dimensions Blueprint<br />\n<a href=\"http://jeffberezny.com/2013/02/12/the-ridiculously-exhaustive-social-media-dimensions-blueprint-infographic/\">View Full Infographic</a></h2>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http://jeffberezny.com/2013/02/12/the-ridiculously-exhaustive-social-media-dimensions-blueprint-infographic/\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-15311\" style=\"border: 1px solid black;\" alt=\"social nework image sizes inforgraphic\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/01/social-nework-image-sizes-inforgraphic.png?resize=600%2C463\" width=\"600\" height=\"463\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/01/social-nework-image-sizes-inforgraphic.png?w=600&amp;ssl=1 600w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/01/social-nework-image-sizes-inforgraphic.png?resize=300%2C231&amp;ssl=1 300w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" /></a></p>\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\">9. How to Get More Likes on Facebook<br />\n<a href=\"http://blog.kissmetrics.com/more-likes-on-facebook/?wide=1\">View Full Infographic</a></h2>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http://blog.kissmetrics.com/more-likes-on-facebook/?wide=1\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-15313\" style=\"border: 1px solid black;\" alt=\"how to get more like on facebook infographic\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/01/how-to-get-more-like-on-facebook-infographic.png?resize=600%2C519\" width=\"600\" height=\"519\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/01/how-to-get-more-like-on-facebook-infographic.png?w=600&amp;ssl=1 600w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/01/how-to-get-more-like-on-facebook-infographic.png?resize=300%2C259&amp;ssl=1 300w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" /></a></p>\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\">10. Twitter Tweet Cheat Sheet<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.mobilemarketingwatch.com/infographic-twitter-cheat-sheet-for-more-followers-engagement-30220/\">View Full Infographic</a></h2>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http://www.mobilemarketingwatch.com/infographic-twitter-cheat-sheet-for-more-followers-engagement-30220/\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-15315\" style=\"border: 1px solid black;\" alt=\"Twitter Tweet Cheat Sheet Infographic\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/01/Twitter-Tweet-Cheat-Sheet-Infographic.png?resize=600%2C462\" width=\"600\" height=\"462\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/01/Twitter-Tweet-Cheat-Sheet-Infographic.png?w=600&amp;ssl=1 600w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/01/Twitter-Tweet-Cheat-Sheet-Infographic.png?resize=300%2C231&amp;ssl=1 300w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" /></a></p>\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\">11. Twiplomacy 2013: How International Organisations Tweet<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.burson-marsteller.com/bm-blog/twiplomacy-infographic-how-international-organizations-tweet/\">View Full Infographic</a></h2>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http://www.burson-marsteller.com/bm-blog/twiplomacy-infographic-how-international-organizations-tweet/\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-15321\" style=\"border: 1px solid black;\" alt=\"international organizations tweet infographic\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/01/international-organizations-tweet-infographic.png?resize=600%2C567\" width=\"600\" height=\"567\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/01/international-organizations-tweet-infographic.png?w=600&amp;ssl=1 600w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/01/international-organizations-tweet-infographic.png?resize=300%2C283&amp;ssl=1 300w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" /></a></p>\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\">12. Social Media for Social Good<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.mediabistro.com/alltwitter/social-media-social-good_b50539\">View Full Infographic</a></h2>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http://www.mediabistro.com/alltwitter/social-media-social-good_b50539\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-15323\" style=\"border: 1px solid black;\" alt=\"social media for social good inforgraphic\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/01/social-media-for-social-good-inforgraphic.png?resize=600%2C607\" width=\"600\" height=\"607\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/01/social-media-for-social-good-inforgraphic.png?w=600&amp;ssl=1 600w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/01/social-media-for-social-good-inforgraphic.png?resize=296%2C300&amp;ssl=1 296w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/01/social-media-for-social-good-inforgraphic.png?resize=75%2C75&amp;ssl=1 75w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" /></a></p>\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\">13. Is My Association Sending Too Much Email?<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.informz.com/blog/am-i-sending-too-much-email/\">View Full Infographic</a></h2>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http://www.informz.com/blog/am-i-sending-too-much-email/\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-15317\" style=\"border: 1px solid black;\" alt=\"email infographic\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/01/email-infographic.png?resize=600%2C606\" width=\"600\" height=\"606\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/01/email-infographic.png?w=600&amp;ssl=1 600w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/01/email-infographic.png?resize=297%2C300&amp;ssl=1 297w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/01/email-infographic.png?resize=75%2C75&amp;ssl=1 75w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" /></a></p>\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\">14. 2013 eNonprofit Benchmarks Study<br />\n<a href=\"http://e-benchmarksstudy.com/?utm_expid=26568703-2.ayzvLestR2GNH4MuCv09qg.0#infographic\">View Full Infographic</a></h2>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http://e-benchmarksstudy.com/?utm_expid=26568703-2.ayzvLestR2GNH4MuCv09qg.0#infographic\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter\" style=\"border: 1px solid black;\" alt=\"2013 eNonprofit Benchmarks Study\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/01/2013-eNonprofit-Benchmarks-Study.png?resize=600%2C414\" width=\"600\" height=\"414\" /></a></p>\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\">15. Architecture of a Donate Page<br />\n<a href=\"http://causepopuli.com/architecture-of-a-donation-page/?goback=.gde_1878448_member_211756643\">View Full Infographic</a></h2>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http://causepopuli.com/architecture-of-a-donation-page\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-15332\" style=\"border: 1px solid black;\" alt=\"the perfect donate landing page infographic\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/01/the-perfect-donate-landing-page-infographic1.png?resize=600%2C415\" width=\"600\" height=\"415\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/01/the-perfect-donate-landing-page-infographic1.png?w=600&amp;ssl=1 600w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/01/the-perfect-donate-landing-page-infographic1.png?resize=300%2C207&amp;ssl=1 300w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" /></a></p>\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\">16. The Digital Giving Index<br />\n<a href=\"http://www1.networkforgood.org/digitalgivingindex\">View Full Infographic</a></h2>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http://www1.networkforgood.org/digitalgivingindex\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-15297\" style=\"border: 1px solid black;\" alt=\"Digital Giving Index\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/01/Digital-Giving-Index.png?resize=600%2C414\" width=\"600\" height=\"414\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/01/Digital-Giving-Index.png?w=600&amp;ssl=1 600w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/01/Digital-Giving-Index.png?resize=300%2C207&amp;ssl=1 300w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" /></a></p>\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\">17. The Rise of the Nonprofit Sector<br />\n<a href=\"http://onlinempa.usfca.edu/infograph-rise-of-noprofit/\">View Full Infographic</a></h2>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http://onlinempa.usfca.edu/infograph-rise-of-noprofit/\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-15327\" style=\"border: 1px solid black;\" alt=\"the rise of the nonprofit sector infographic\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/01/the-rise-of-the-nonprofit-sector-infographic.png?resize=600%2C505\" width=\"600\" height=\"505\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/01/the-rise-of-the-nonprofit-sector-infographic.png?w=600&amp;ssl=1 600w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/01/the-rise-of-the-nonprofit-sector-infographic.png?resize=300%2C252&amp;ssl=1 300w\" siz